task.summary: * created vital methods for client operations * created message-related utilities
replaced tiff.h dependency with stdint.h ( uint{XX} --> uint{XX}_t )

* finished explode(), implode(), inspect() and isEqual() methods of utils.c * finished generateMessage() and generateRandomMessage() of client.c * slight refactorings to remove auto-added file headers by CLion
renamed entry file from app.c --> main.c
* added getPendingMessages() and hasPendingMessages() methods' signatures in server.c * added receive() and send() methods' signatures in client.c

* added meta fields in Message struct * added mac2hex() and hex2mac() methods in utils.c * fixed memory leaks in utils.c and client.c methods * added RNG initial seeding * added draft of necessary server methods, receiveAll(), transmitAll() and transmit() * code quality improvements
* added Device type in utils.h * added fundamental server methods in server.c: receive(), receiveAll(), transmit() and transmitAll() * commented out previous server implementation

* re-organized code base in distinct directories for header and C files * added Makefile to compile using "make all" * added timestamp2ftime() to convert UNIX timestamp to human-readable date * minor documentation updates & fixed
